articles.title: Bonfire and beers: How Cameron Smith celebrated winning THE PLAYERS Championship - PGA TOUR
articles.description: PONTE VEDRA BEACH, Fla. – It was late Monday evening when THE PLAYERS Championship winner Cameron Smith arrived back at his beautiful waterfront home about 15 minutes down the road from TPC Sawgrass with the iconic gold man trophy in his grasp.
